370
00:20:12.570 --> 00:20:14.670
I then, all smarting with mywounds being cold,

371
00:20:14.670 --> 00:20:16.170
to be so pester'd with apopinjay,

372
00:20:16.170 --> 00:20:17.670
out of my grief and myimpatience

